msgctxt "172_The Florist"
msgid "While you've been looking for me, I've had my eye on you.\\r\n"\n"So, is there something you wanted to ask me?"
msgstr "Mientras me buscabas, the he estado observando.\\r\n"\n"Dime, ¿Querías preguntarme algo?"

msgctxt "184_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "196_Saejima"
msgid "(Time for some answers...)"
msgstr "(Es hora de unas respuestas...)."

msgctxt "208_Saejima"
msgid "So what's the deal with this Purgatory joint?"
msgstr "Así que, ¿Cuál es el asunto con este antro?"

msgctxt "220_The Florist"
msgid "You know that entertainment area you saw as you came in?"
msgstr "¿Viste el área de entretenimiento cuando entraste?"

msgctxt "232_Saejima"
msgid "Kinda hard to miss."
msgstr "Dificil de ignorar."

msgctxt "244_The Florist"
msgid "Well, I built it myself years ago. What you see, I created."
msgstr "Bueno, yo mismo la construí hace años. Lo que ves, yo lo creé."

msgctxt "256_The Florist"
msgid "Kamurocho's rich and famous come here from all quarters\\r\n"\n"for a taste of the pleasures they can't get aboveground."
msgstr "Los adinerados y famosos de Kamurocho vienen aqui por una probada\\r\n"\n"de los placeres que no se encuentran en la superficie."

msgctxt "268_The Florist"
msgid "We cater to every taste, no matter how decadent.\\r\n"\n"Gambling, sex, things of that nature."
msgstr "Nos adaptamos a cada gusto, no importa lo sucios que sean.\\r\n"\n"Apuestas, sexo, cosas por el estilo."

msgctxt "280_The Florist"
msgid "Normally, potential clients are carefully screened before\\r\n"\n"I let them in, though I've made an exception in your case."
msgstr "Normalmente, los clientes son examinados cuidadosamente antes\\r\n"\n"de permitirles la entrada, aunque he hecho una excepción en tu caso."

msgctxt "292_The Florist"
msgid "But these pleasures are going to cost you. Just be careful\\r\n"\n"the place doesn't suck you in. Don't forget, you're a man\\r\n"\n"on a mission."
msgstr "Pero estos placeres cuestan. Cuidado con distraerte.\\r\n"\n"No lo olvides, tienes una misión."

msgctxt "316_Saejima"
msgid "Folks call you some kinda info broker."
msgstr "La gente dice que das información."

msgctxt "328_The Florist"
msgid "That they do. I'm a dealer, and the drug I sell is intel."
msgstr "Así es. Soy un traficante y la droga que vendo es información."

msgctxt "340_The Florist"
msgid "Information on everything that goes down in Kamurocho\\r\n"\n"eventually reaches my ears, one way or another."
msgstr "Información sobre todo lo que sucede en Kamurocho\\r\n"\n"eventualmente llega a mi, de una u otra forma."

msgctxt "352_The Florist"
msgid "I have a network of informers at my fingertips\\r\n"\n"and surveillance cameras mounted all over town.\\r\n"\n"I've got eyes in every nook and cranny."
msgstr "Tengo una red de informantes a la palma de mi mano\\r\n"\n"y camaras de vigilancia por toda la ciudad.\\r\n"\n"Tengo ojos en cada rincón de la ciudad."

msgctxt "400_The Florist"
msgid "You being here means there's something you want to know.\\r\n"\n"Something only I can find out for you."
msgstr "Tu presencia solo significa que quieres saber algo.\\r\n"\n"Algo que solo yo puedo averiguar por ti."

msgctxt "412_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah. I'm lookin' for Hideki Sasai, Patriarch of the Sasai\\r\n"\n"Family－or at least he was back in '85. Know where he's at?"
msgstr "Sí. Estoy buscando a Hideki Sasai, patriarca de la familia Sasai\\r\n"\n"allá por el '85. ¿Sabes dónde está?"

msgctxt "424_The Florist"
msgid "I do, but my intel doesn't come cheap."
msgstr "Lo hago, pero mi información no es regalada."

msgctxt "436_Saejima"
msgid "Name your price."
msgstr "Di tu precio."

msgctxt "448_The Florist"
msgid "Let's say 10 million yen."
msgstr "Podriamos decir 10 millones de yenes."

msgctxt "460_Saejima"
msgid "That a joke?"
msgstr "¿Es una broma?"

msgctxt "472_Saejima"
msgid "I ain't holdin' that kinda cash. But you already knew that,\\r\n"\n"didn't ya?"
msgstr "No tengo tanto dinero. Pero ya lo sabías, ¿Verdad?"

msgctxt "484_The Florist"
msgid "Of course. I wouldn't be much of an info dealer\\r\n"\n"if I didn't. But you do have another option.\\r\n"\n"There's something you can do for me instead."
msgstr "Por supuesto. Si no, no sería informante.\\r\n"\n"Pero no tienes otra opción. Quiero que hagas algo por mi."

msgctxt "496_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah? Let's hear it."
msgstr "Sí, oigámoslas."

msgctxt "508_The Florist"
msgid "Heh... Follow me."
msgstr "Claro. Sígueme."

